	<text>
		<body>
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001105_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'--> 
<!--Hand 01 17 top left--><!--Hand 02 56360 top right-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Carlisle</placeName> 3<hi rend="sup">d</hi><choice><abbr>Oct<hi rend="sup">r</hi></abbr><expan>October</expan></choice></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1857</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear Sir</p>
<lb/><p>Your favour 
<lb/>of the 26<hi rend="sup">th</hi><choice><abbr>ult</abbr><expan>ultimo</expan></choice> has 
<lb/>just come to 
<lb/>hand but no 
<lb/>portraits. They 
<lb/>may have gone 
<lb/>to Glasgow 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001105_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'--> 
<lb/>but ought to have 
<lb/>been here before 
<lb/>this. If they 
<lb/>come within 
<lb/>the next 3 or 4 
<lb/>days I shall 
<lb/>write &amp; let you 
<lb/>know.</p>
<lb/><p>If you are 
<lb/>near <persName>Oliver &amp; Boyd</persName>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001105_0003"/><!--pb/@n='3'--> 
<lb/>would you kindly 
<lb/>say to them that 
<lb/>my address for 
<lb/>the next 5 days 
<lb/>will be <placeName>Kendal 
<lb/>Westmoreland</placeName> where 
<lb/>they may send 
<lb/>a packet of letters 
<lb/>Mr. Murray writes 
<lb/>about if that 
<lb/>was not the same 
<lb/>which was put 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001105_0004"/><!--pb/@n='4'--> 
<lb/>into my hands in 
<lb/>Edinburgh</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">I am &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p>David Livingstone</p>
<lb/><p><persName>T B. Johnston Esq</persName></p>
			
